text: Kaffrine is a region in the center of Senegal. The regional capital is Kaffrine. As of the 2013 census, 544,011 people lived there. It has an area of . It was created in 2008. == Départements == There are four départements: * Birkilane Département * Kaffrine Département * Koungheul Département * Malem Hoddar Département Category:2008 establishments in Africa Category:Regions of Senegal
title: Kaffrine Region
